<br />
avail at a decent price at one of the local comp stores.
<br />

<br />
At this time the idea of hours of raids to kill off  coirnav and then the rathe council /not sure which is first to be honest. Then the months long farming of time makes me cringe.  Thats simply more time than I have and am willing to sacrafice and if you do have the time and inclination to gear up in time /cheer.
